    <title type="html"><![CDATA[在GoDaddy设置域名跳转]]></title>
    <link href="http://rinh.github.com/blog/2012/09/04/zai-godaddyshe-zhi-yu-ming-tiao-zhuan/"/>
    <updated>2012-09-04T11:03:00+08:00</updated>
